{"word":"ἡμερεύω","slug":"ἡμερεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἡμερεύω</b></el> <el>(ἡμερεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἡμέρα'><el>ἡμέρα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to spend the day</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: —<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to travel the whole day</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to pass one's days, live</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}